		<li>  
			<div class="large-img"><a href="/content/38178" target="_blank"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://hvasl.ir/sites/default/files/styles/160_160/public/news/1396/12/26/1218497337.jpg?itok=tNGHGG34" width="160" height="160" alt="" /></a>				<span class="text-large-img">
						
				</span>
			</div>
			
			
			<div class="info-box" >
									<div class="surtitle">با حضور ابراهیم حاتمی کیا؛</div>
