			<div class="large-img"><a href="/content/38135" target="_blank"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="http://hvasl.ir/sites/default/files/styles/160_160/public/news/1396/12/23/634533425.jpg?itok=5go6JHnG" width="160" height="160" alt="" /></a>				<span class="text-large-img">
						
				</span>
